            "summary": "A focused workspace interface for AI-assisted work, combining a clean canvas with contextual tools and project organization.",
            "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>AI Workspace</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg: #FFF8F0;\n      --card: #FFF;\n      --accent: #FF8C69;\n      --text: #4A3E38;\n      --muted: #A1887F;\n      --radius: 16px;\n      --space: 20px;\n    }\n    * {\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n    body {\n      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n      background: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      font-size: 16px;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n    .container {\n      width: 100%;\n      max-width: 375px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      min-height: 667px;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      background: var(--bg);\n    }\n    .header {\n      padding: var(--space);\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #E8DDD5;\n      background: var(--card);\n    }\n    .header h1 {\n      font-size: 28px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n    .header p {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n    }\n    .main {\n      flex: 1;\n      padding: var(--space);\n      overflow-y: auto;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: var(--space);\n    }\n    .canvas-section {\n      background: var(--card);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      padding: var(--space);\n      min-height: 240px;\n      border: 2px dashed var(--muted);\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      font-size: 14px;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    .projects-section {\n      background: var(--card);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      padding: var(--space);\n    }\n    .section-title {\n      font-size: 18px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\n      color: var(--text);\n    }\n    .project-item {\n      padding: 12px;\n      background: var(--bg);\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);\n      cursor: pointer;\n      transition: background 0.2s;\n    }\n    .project-item:hover {\n      background: #F5EBE0;\n    }\n    .project-name {\n      font-size: 16px;\n      font-weight: 500;\n      color: var(--text);\n    }\n    .project-meta {\n      font-size: 12px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      margin-top: 4px;\n    }\n    .footer {\n      padding: var(--space);\n      border-top: 1px solid #E8DDD5;\n      background: var(--card);\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 8px;\n    }\n    .btn {\n      flex: 1;\n      padding: 12px 16px;\n      border: none;\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      transition: all 0.2s;\n    }\n    .btn-primary {\n      background: var(--accent);\n      color: #FFF;\n    }\n    .btn-primary:hover {\n      background: #E67A52;\n    }\n    .btn-secondary {\n      background: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      border: 1px solid #E8DDD5;\n    }\n    .btn-secondary:hover {\n      background: #F5EBE0;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"header\">\n      <h1>Workspace</h1>\n      <p>Start a new task or continue working</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"main\">\n      <div class=\"canvas-section\">\n        Tap to begin writing or paste content\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"projects-section\">\n        <div class=\"section-title\">Recent Projects</div>\n        <div class=\"project-item\">\n          <div class=\"project-name\">Research Brief</div>\n          <div class=\"project-meta\">Last edited 2 hours ago</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"project-item\">\n          <div class=\"project-name\">Product Outline</div>\n          <div class=\"project-meta\">Last edited yesterday</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"project-item\">\n         